26
00:04:28,541 --> 00:04:29,583
- HOW IS HE?

27
00:04:29,666 --> 00:04:30,833
- IS ROY ANY BETTER, MOM?

28
00:04:33,333 --> 00:04:36,625
- HE HASN'T EATEN ANYTHING
