34
00:05:30,708 --> 00:05:32,833
- I LOVE 'EM, DADDY.
THEY'RE SO PRETTY.

35
00:05:32,916 --> 00:05:34,083
- Roy: GOOD.

36
00:06:07,500 --> 00:06:08,583
RITA.

37
00:06:12,875 --> 00:06:14,083
( crying ) RITA.

38
00:06:15,916 --> 00:06:17,083
RITA.

39
00:06:18,875 --> 00:06:20,000
RITA!

40
00:06:25,625 --> 00:06:26,583
- ( sighs )

