44
00:06:36,250 --> 00:06:38,000
SOURCES CLOSE TO
THE CASE, HOWEVER,

45
00:06:38,083 --> 00:06:40,916
INDICATE THAT AN AS YET
UNIDENTIFIED INDIVIDUAL

46
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:42,083
WAS WITNESSED ATOP THE TOWER

47
00:06:42,166 --> 00:06:43,708
JUST MOMENTS
BEFORE ITS COLLAPSE.

48
00:06:43,791 --> 00:06:44,958
- Ashley: JEREMY KOLBEL.

49
00:06:46,750 --> 00:06:48,208
FOOLISH GIRL.

50
00:06:48,291 --> 00:06:51,083
YOU SEE THE TROUBLE YOU CAUSE
WHEN YOU GO AGAINST R.U.C.

51
00:06:53,000 --> 00:06:55,041
HOWEVER, YOUR
RECKLESS AMBITION

52
00:06:55,125 --> 00:06:57,583
HAS PROVEN TO BE
QUITE USEFUL TO ME.

53
00:07:05,541 --> 00:07:07,083
- JEREMY.

54
00:07:07,166 --> 00:07:08,625
- IT'S NOT YOUR FAULT, YUTO.

55
00:07:08,708 --> 00:07:10,916
YOU DID EVERYTHING
YOU COULD TO STOP HER.

56
00:07:11,000 --> 00:07:13,208
DON'T BLAME YOURSELF FOR THIS.

57
00:07:13,291 --> 00:07:16,750
- BUT, SHE WAS MY FRIEND AND
NOW ROSE IS DEAD BECAUSE OF HER.

